DEPENDENCIES
------------

+ eBox components

	+ ebox
	+ ebox-network
	+ ebox-firewall

+ Debian packages (apt-get install <package>)

	+ libtree-perl
	+ iptables
	+ iproute

+ Others

	+ a Netfilter enabled Linux kernel
	+ a QoS enabled Linux kernel

INSTALLATION
------------

- Once all dependencies are satisfied, type:
	
	./configure
	make install

  configure will autodetect eBox base path to install

- Reload apache daemon

        pkill apache